<item>
            <title>[LU-1134] nfs tests bypass lustre setup</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1134</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In our nfs tests today, it&apos;s assuming that lustre should be setup and mount. This is not true in autotest env anymore. We need to figure out a best way to deal with this&lt;/p&gt;

